---

<Layout
  title="High-End & Luxury Appliance Repair Beverly Hills"
  description="Book Online (424) 499-7788 ★★★★★ High-End & Luxury appliance repair in Beverly Hills for Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, La Cornue and other premium brands. Same-day or next-day service."
  structuredData={structuredData}
  ogImage="/high-end-and-luxury-appliance-repair-by-zaricci.webp"
>
  <ParallaxHeader client:idle />

  <div class="maincontent" id="webpage">
    <h2>Luxury Appliance Repair in Beverly Hills, CA</h2>

    <p>
      In Beverly Hills, appliance repair is often performed inside carefully designed estates,
      hillside residences, renovated luxury homes, and high-end condos with premium built-in
      kitchens. Homes throughout the Central Area, Hillside Area, and Trousdale Estates frequently
      feature panel-ready refrigerators, professional ranges, wall ovens, wine storage systems,
      outdoor kitchens, and European appliance brands that require precise diagnostics, clean
      workmanship, and a careful repair approach.
    </p>

    <p>
      From residences near Beverly Gardens Park and the streets surrounding the Rodeo Drive
      corridor to hillside properties and custom homes in Trousdale Estates, we provide service
      designed around the needs of luxury appliances and the finishes that surround them.
    </p>
  </div>

  <Tabs client:visible />

  <div class="maincontent" id="service">
    <section>
      <h3>Why Beverly Hills Homeowners Rely on ZARICCI</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>✅ Trained in Major Luxury Brands</strong>
          <br />
          We specialize in high-performance, fully integrated, and smart appliances—whether
          you are working with a dual-fuel Wolf range, a panel-ready Sub-Zero refrigerator,
          or a Miele steam oven. Our technicians use a careful, brand-conscious diagnostic
          approach for premium appliances.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ OEM Parts Whenever Available</strong>
          <br />
          Your appliances are an investment. When replacement components are needed, we
          identify the appropriate OEM, manufacturer-approved, or compatible part for the
          specific appliance and model.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Same-Day or Next-Day Scheduling</strong>
          <br />
          We offer priority scheduling in Beverly Hills whenever appointment availability
          allows, with respect for your time, privacy, and home.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Discreet, White-Glove Repair Experience</strong>
          <br />
          We maintain a clean workspace, work carefully around cabinetry and flooring, and
          communicate with the professionalism expected in a luxury home.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Our Luxury Repair Process</h3>

      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Book Your Appointment</strong>
          <br />
          Call or schedule online. We will confirm your preferred time and gather basic
          information about your appliance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>On-Time Arrival & Brand-Specific Diagnosis</strong>
          <br />
          Your ZARICCI technician arrives promptly and performs a careful inspection using
          the diagnostic approach appropriate for the appliance type and symptoms.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear, Upfront Estimate</strong>
          <br />
          We explain the issue and provide a transparent quote before proceeding with the
          recommended repair.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Precision Repair & Performance Testing</strong>
          <br />
          We complete the approved repair, restore appliance function, and test the relevant
          systems for proper performance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Final Walkthrough & Service Warranty</strong>
          <br />
          We clean the work area, answer your questions, and explain the warranty that applies
          to the completed service.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Serving Beverly Hills Homes and Estates</h3>

      <p>
        We serve residences throughout the Central Area, Hillside Area, Trousdale Estates,
        the Beverly Hills Flats, and residential streets near Beverly Gardens Park, Roxbury
        Drive, North Beverly Drive, Canon Drive, and Coldwater Canyon Drive. Our service is
        designed for custom estates, hillside properties, luxury condos, and carefully
        renovated kitchens where precise diagnostics, clean workmanship, and discretion matter.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Your Home Deserves More Than a Quick Fix</h3>

      <p>
        Your luxury appliances were selected for their performance, craftsmanship, and style.
        At <strong>ZARICCI</strong>, we deliver a repair experience that reflects those same
        values—with skill, discretion, and careful service from start to finish.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>📞 Schedule Your Luxury Appliance Repair in Beverly Hills Today</h3>

      <p>
        Do not wait for a small appliance issue to become a major disruption.
        <br />
        Call <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> or book online now to
        schedule expert service in Beverly Hills, CA.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>ZARICCI — Because Beverly Hills Homes Deserve World-Class Repair.</strong>
      </p>
    </section>

    <Logos client:visible />
    <Reviews client:idle />
  </div>
</Layout>